# CHANGELOG

## v0.1.13 - 22 Jul 2024

Bump for default image tag

## v0.1.12 - 17 Jul 2024

Bump for default image tag

## v0.1.10 - 12 Jul 2024

Fix bug in Ingress

## v0.1.8 - 01 Jul 2024

Update the chart to more closely align with nim-llm

## v0.1.6 - 28 Jun 2024

Update default modelID for precompiled model

## v0.1.5 - 26 Jun 2024

Update default modelID for precompiled model

## v0.1.4 - 25 Jun 2024

Stabilize chart and include instructions for snowflake arctic

## v0.1.3 - 24 Jun 2024

Modification to allow for dynamic PersistentVolume provisioners
Allow configuration of the ephemeral workspace size

## v0.1.2 - 7 Jun 2024

Modify download model job to be an init container.
Add model compilation step with caching.
Add ability to download git lfs models to the PVC.
Add ability to configure the storage class of the PVC.
Add ability to override the template file.
Add ability to override OTEL configuration
Add chart dependencies to allow the container to run standalone

## v0.1.0 - 9 Apr 2024

Initial version
